{"type":"text","timestamp":1775845214059,"sessionID":"ses_28761b670ffennREmll7mYgy2n","part":{"id":"prt_d789f4cd6001N9RV0otOHuX2v3","messageID":"msg_d789f42a5001EA9pIwIMZrvXrA","sessionID":"ses_28761b670ffennREmll7mYgy2n","type":"text","text":"Based on my review of the AR-006 implementation, here is the archive summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 (Sandbox Deletion & Lifecycle Management)\n\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Status:** Completed ✅\n\n### Completed\n\n1. **GarbageCollector Implementation** (`garbage_collector.go:33-154`)\n   - `GarbageCollector` struct with dynamic client, store client, interval, and context\n   - `Start()` / `Stop()` methods for lifecycle management\n   - `gcLoop()` - periodic cleanup loop with ticker\n   - `tick()` - single cleanup cycle that checks idle and expired sandboxes\n   - `deleteSandbox()` - unified sandbox deletion logic\n   - `recordAudit()` - audit logging for cleanup operations\n\n2. **HTTP Handler** (`handler/sandbox.go:19-74`)\n   - `SandboxHandler` struct\n   - `HandleDeleteSandbox()` - manual deletion API endpoint\n   - Proper error handling for missing sessions\n   - Sandbox vs SandboxClaim resource type detection\n\n3. **Controller Layer** (`controller/sandbox.go:254-276`)\n   - `DeleteSession()` method in `SandboxController`\n   - Retrieves sandbox info, deletes K8s resources, cleans up store\n\n4. **Type Definitions** (`types/sandbox_types.go`)\n   - `DeleteSandboxResponse` struct\n   - `SandboxCleanupReason` type with constants (Manual, IdleTimeout, Expired)\n   - `CleanupAuditEntry` struct for audit logging\n\n5. **Resource Group Definitions** (`garbage_collector.go:19-31`)\n   - `SandboxGVR` - for agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes\n   - `SandboxClaimGVR` - for extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims\n\n6. **Store Interface Extension** (`store/store.go:25-26, 143-184`)\n   - `ListExpiredSandboxes()` - queries sandboxes past expiration\n   - `ListInactiveSandboxes()` - queries sandboxes past idle threshold\n\n7. **Unit Tests** (`garbage_collector_test.go`)\n   - Mock store implementation\n   - Tests for idle sandbox cleanup\n   - Tests for expired sandbox cleanup\n   - Tests for error handling\n\n8. **Configuration Constants** (`defaults.go`)\n   - `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` (15 minutes)\n   - `GCInterval` (15 seconds)\n   - `GCSingleTickTimeout` (2 minutes)\n   - `DeleteTimeout` (30 seconds)\n\n### Deferred\n\n1. **Metrics/Observability** (design.md:717-744)\n   - Prometheus metrics (`workloadmanager_gc_deleted_total`, `workloadmanager_gc_failed_total`, `workloadmanager_gc_duration_seconds`)\n   - No implementation found\n\n2. **RBAC Configuration** (design.md:770-783)\n   - Required permissions YAML not implemented in code\n\n3. **Integration Tests** (design.md:673-712)\n   - End-to-end lifecycle tests not present\n\n4. **Future Enhancements** (design.md:841-847)\n   - Graceful shutdown with preStop hooks\n   - Dependency cleanup (Secrets, ConfigMaps, PVCs)\n   - Bulk deletion API\n   - Deletion webhooks\n   - Deletion policies (foreground/background)\n   - Snapshot/persist before deletion\n\n5. **API Response Type Mismatch**\n   - Design specifies `DeleteSessionResponse` with `sessionId` + `deletedAt`\n   - Implementation uses `DeleteSandboxResponse` with `message` only","time":{"start":1775845214055,"end":1775845214055}}}
